window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A hitman must be anonymous, amoral...and alone. </p> <p>Victor is the face in the crowd you don't see, a perfect assassin with nothing to live for. </p> <p>But when an old friend turns to him for help, he finds he can't refuse. For once his objective isn't to kill but to protect. </p> <p>Hunted through the streets of London by ruthless enemies, Victor needs to be more than just a bodyguard...but his every move leads danger closer to the very person he's vowed to defend. </p> <p><b>Published in the US as <i>No Tomorrow</i>.</b> </p>"; 
